data.description: Better than brand new! SELLLER TO OFFER $3K TOWARDS BUYER’S CLOSING COSTS. Lived in for less than a year with lots of upgrades. New fencing, interior finishes, new shed, landscaping and much more. Very well laid out 2 or 3 bedroom home with two full bathrooms and separate laundry room. Very cozy and well appointed on a private setting. Soak in the peaceful country views on your covered front porch. Fenced in back yard perfect for pets. This home is prestine and move in ready.
